Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.95,0:00:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.72,0:00:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦总有醒来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.13,0:00:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是甜蜜的绮梦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.59,0:00:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抑或可怕的噩梦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.41,0:00:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都会在温暖的被窝中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.66,0:00:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在妈妈的呼唤中 梦会终结
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.62,0:00:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日复一日...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.37,0:00:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎来的都是一成不变的晨景
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.16,0:00:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.55,0:00:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}不知从何时起 梦境便开始永无尽头...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再哭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.69,0:02:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.25,0:02:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是说话啊 亚由亚由
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜咕 我才不叫亚由亚由呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.37,0:02:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 原来你能说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.41,0:02:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样看着我 我也很为难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.23,0:02:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成 我长得和你失散了的哥哥一模一样？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我差不多该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.21,0:02:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肚子饿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.79,0:02:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是饿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.10,0:02:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.19,0:02:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 去买点什么吃的给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.32,0:02:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想吃什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有吗 喜欢吃的东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.72,0:02:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鯛鱼烧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.25,0:03:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吃鯛鱼烧是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.67,0:03:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那你在这里等着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.71,0:03:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}第４话\N假日之奇想曲\N～caprice～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有好好在这里等着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.94,0:03:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你叫我在这等着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.12,0:03:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.15,0:03:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.55,0:03:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还很热呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.45,0:03:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鯛鱼烧可是刚烧出来的最好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.77,0:03:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃啊 你也吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.45,0:04:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是咸的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.62,0:04:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你刚才流的眼泪的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.59,0:04:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时侯的我啊 真是急的要命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.38,0:04:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才为什么在哭？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.30,0:04:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 你不想说的话今天我就不问了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.49,0:04:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差不多要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.30,0:04:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 亚由亚由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.33,0:04:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 不叫亚由亚由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.23,0:04:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这...样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.83,0:04:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.14,0:04:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我可走不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.12,0:04:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鯛鱼烧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.28,0:05:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想再吃鯛鱼烧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.42,0:05:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那么喜欢吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.39,0:05:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么下次再一起吃吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.55,0:05:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 明天这时候我在车站前的长凳那里等你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.15,0:05:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不骗我？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.55,0:05:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不骗你 我一定会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.09,0:05:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.28,0:05:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们拉勾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.87,0:05:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用拉勾我也会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜咕 拉勾...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉勾勾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.55,0:05:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.71,0:05:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.63,0:06:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.67,0:06:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.46,0:06:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.47,0:06:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.30,0:07:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜 吓死我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.22,0:07:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想来报复我 没想到又失败了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.75,0:07:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.85,0:07:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个蒟蒻你打算做夜宵吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.32,0:07:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.30,0:07:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.52,0:07:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是要吃才拿在手上的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.81,0:07:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有味道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.89,0:07:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大口大口吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.29,0:07:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了 我已经很饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.57,0:07:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪费粮食可是要遭报应的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.60,0:07:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.64,0:07:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.04,0:07:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴在吃蒟蒻 说是当夜宵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.70,0:07:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒟蒻？你有那么饿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.87,0:07:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 我去做点东西给你吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.98,0:07:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不饿了...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.43,0:07:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不错呢 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.34,0:07:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.94,0:08:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 扰人清梦也要有个限度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定要把这些整理完
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.59,0:08:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.86,0:08:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早上是用「啊呜」跟人打招呼的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胃一直疼到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.13,0:08:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫你半夜还闹着要吃东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.90,0:08:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是用来往你脸上...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.23,0:08:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要对我的脸怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.32,0:08:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你走着瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.37,0:08:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.60,0:08:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要去购物吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.06,0:08:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 另外名雪忘带便当了 我打算帮她送去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子今天也有田径部的练习
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.76,0:09:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就让我去送吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田径部的部长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在社团里会是一副什么样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.24,0:09:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你帮我送来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.53,0:09:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个体育馆还真够壮观的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.83,0:09:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这所学校可是很重视社团活动的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.79,0:09:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.96,0:09:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为快要比赛了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.71,0:10:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.43,0:10:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以稍微看一会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.82,0:10:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 站在角落看就没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.89,0:10:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.82,0:10:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相泽君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是要去参加社团活动？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.80,0:10:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名雪也好，你也好，休息日还那么认真
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.13,0:10:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是名雪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.23,0:10:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是不想呆在家里而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.26,0:10:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和父母吵架了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.56,0:10:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.24,0:11:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相泽君 学校的生活习惯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然才上了几天课 也算是多少习惯了点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.18,0:11:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也幸亏在一个教室里有认识的人在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指名雪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.17,0:11:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可不要给名雪添太多麻烦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.54,0:11:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏她你才能融入到班级里去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.56,0:11:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你要好好谢谢她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.66,0:11:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.91,0:11:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名雪虽说经常一副满不在乎的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.56,0:11:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有时也会很勉强自己 你要多关心她一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.22,0:11:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社团活动也是每天都练到筋疲力尽为止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.06,0:11:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她那么能睡原来是因为这个的原因吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.37,0:11:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得那是天生的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.01,0:11:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.78,0:11:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋子阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思 难得的假期还要你帮我做这做那的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 这点小事没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:12:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些都要秋子阿姨一个人搬也太累了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 有祐一真是帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.75,0:12:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.56,0:12:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是祐一君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.55,0:12:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们又见面了……呜哇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.81,0:12:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜咕 又撞到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.74,0:12:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次可不关我的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.74,0:12:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.21,0:12:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是祐一的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.01,0:12:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不认识的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜咕 真过分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.76,0:12:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.97,0:12:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道祐一讨厌我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.51,0:12:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也吃霸王餐了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.48,0:12:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是刚才卖鯛鱼烧的爷爷送给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.94,0:12:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明给人家添了那么多麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是个老好人的爷爷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.06,0:12:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很活泼的女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.26,0:12:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是水瀬秋子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是收留我住的户主
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,户主是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.11,0:13:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指家里地位最高的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.34,0:13:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又学到新知识了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.65,0:13:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 能给我也介绍一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月宫亚由
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.02,0:13:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.89,0:13:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月宫亚由？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.50,0:13:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的心理作用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.80,0:13:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一  接下来你要做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.56,0:13:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正准备回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定要把搬家的行李收拾了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我去帮你收拾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.91,0:13:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.74,0:13:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨天有帮我找东西 这就当作报答吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.36,0:13:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.51,0:13:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:13:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄得还真淑女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.54,0:14:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为你会像往常一样一头冲进来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事我很少做...呀~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.39,0:14:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.89,0:14:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快出来吧 我来帮你们介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.20,0:14:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.49,0:14:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽渡真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.17,0:14:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我一样也借住在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那样子可是很吓人的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起码要下来和人打个招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫月宫亚由 请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.96,0:14:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽...泽渡真琴 多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.51,0:14:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也巧 你也顺便来帮我一起整理行李吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.40,0:15:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴也要吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.70,0:15:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁让你也是借住的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮忙整理一下总可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.50,0:15:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴 不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.69,0:15:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.59,0:15:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是没力气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.53,0:15:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你管
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.39,0:15:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来这里就是祐一君的房间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.35,0:15:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死了 已经筋疲力尽了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.27,0:15:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才只搬了一个而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.84,0:15:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的我来搬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.44,0:15:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们就把里面的东西拿出来整理一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.13,0:15:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.07,0:15:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃吗？ 鯛鱼烧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.49,0:15:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.74,0:15:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点凉了 你不介意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.42,0:16:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好甜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.41,0:16:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不喜欢甜食吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.03,0:16:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 当心变胖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.91,0:16:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.36,0:16:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说太累了 待会再来吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然三人一起动手很快就整理好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.49,0:16:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟真琴好像只是在把行李搬来搬去而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.03,0:16:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜咕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.36,0:16:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过至少有帮上一点忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.61,0:17:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 多亏你们帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.13,0:17:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说好要来帮忙结果什么忙都没帮上的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.59,0:17:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就搞得我好像在骗人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.31,0:17:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚由 要找的东西找到没有？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.58,0:17:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.64,0:17:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.95,0:17:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 虽然不清楚是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.48,0:17:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她好像在找什么很重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.05,0:17:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前几天祐一帮我找过 所以今天这也算是回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.53,0:17:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 能快点找到就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.42,0:17:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.65,0:17:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人可以回去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.70,0:17:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想跟真琴道个别...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.89,0:17:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定还在睡午觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.66,0:17:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后随时欢迎你再来玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.17,0:18:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 那再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.91,0:18:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要来吃蛋糕吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.95,0:18:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.25,0:18:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.80,0:18:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.30,0:18:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是来帮我按摩吗 真是麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.35,0:18:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.43,0:18:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那等我洗好澡再找你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.05,0:18:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是来给你按摩的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.19,0:19:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来取上次借给你的笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.66,0:19:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的笔记？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.46,0:19:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是借给你了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.67,0:19:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你说这里的进度比你以前的学校快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.18,0:19:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把它放在学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.69,0:19:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还要做作业呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.87,0:19:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉 明天到学校再还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.03,0:19:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.83,0:19:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说再见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.48,0:19:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也别说回见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.40,0:19:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你要我怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.32,0:19:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我要说的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么办才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.94,0:19:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天再想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.28,0:19:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚就早点去睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了明天就来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.48,0:19:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一你要是没法做作业的话也会很为难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.34,0:19:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已是一个超脱于这些俗事之外的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没你那么超脱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个老师很严厉的 不把作业好好完成一定会挨骂的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.35,0:19:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你是想我现在去学校把笔记拿回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是这个意思...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.52,0:20:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我去一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.74,0:20:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校应该已经关门了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.46,0:20:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总会有几扇窗户开着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.70,0:20:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没开着的话我就敲碎玻璃进去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.68,0:20:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以那样...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面很冷的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.66,0:20:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  我就顺便当是散步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.81,0:20:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.61,0:20:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香里叮嘱过我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.94,0:20:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以给你添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 因为我要你跑两趟学校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.22,0:20:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我自作自受 你不用介意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.68,0:20:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的星星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.84,0:21:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快点回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.40,0:23:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是讨伐魔物之人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.79,0:23:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以说 小鬼 给我退学吧 之类的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.88,0:23:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要做那种事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.86,0:23:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨伐魔物之人讨伐魔物之人讨伐魔物...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.67,0:23:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋子小姐的料理手艺真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.21,0:23:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有机会你可以尝尝她的特制果酱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.99,0:24:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想吃些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.47,0:24:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一先生真的像是哥哥一样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.25,0:24:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为会被杀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.12,0:24:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来这里做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.07,0:24:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.00,0:24:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(350,0)\an8\fs26}第5话\N群魔的小夜曲\N～serecade～
